  "short_description": "Table Tennis Toon is a fast-paced table tennis game. Aim with complete freedom and fire the ball with five different types of shot! Choose your character and play solo or against your friends in thrilling and adrenaline-fuelled matches. Prevail and conquer the title of \"Ping Pong Master\"!",
