  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Table Tennis Toon!</strong> is a fast-paced table tennis game. The peculiarity is that unlike other ping pong games you can <strong>aim precisely</strong> thanks to the movable viewfinder on the table. The quality of your shots depends completely on your <strong>positioning</strong> and <strong>timing</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>five</strong> different types of shot or a <strong>combination</strong> of these! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, you read right! You can make a shot combining Topspin and Rightspin effects for example!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The five shots are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accuracy Shot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Topspin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backspin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sidespin Right</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sidespin Left</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try different characters, everyone with his unique set of stats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are four stats:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you choose a balanced character or will you go with a specialized one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>Story Mode</strong>! Choose your favorite character and guide their unique journey to become the \"Ping Pong Master\". Face all other opponents in a series of matches enriched with fun dialogues that reveal the motivations and rivalries of each champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in split-screen with your friends for the best experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is nothing more satisfying than smashing the ball against your friend or hitting the edge of the table at the set point!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or Play Online with your Steam friends using Steam Remote Play Together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0c23c6a24cda88acfa0fa64171aa2880.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=224 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0e74567ef1599640d3fe37886c6e3e3d.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Table Tennis Toon!</strong> is a fast-paced table tennis game. The peculiarity is that unlike other ping pong games you can <strong>aim precisely</strong> thanks to the movable viewfinder on the table. The quality of your shots depends completely on your <strong>positioning</strong> and <strong>timing</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>five</strong> different types of shot or a <strong>combination</strong> of these! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, you read right! You can make a shot combining Topspin and Rightspin effects for example!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The five shots are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accuracy Shot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Topspin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backspin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sidespin Right</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sidespin Left</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/4899eee7681228184f33c1b6aedaef42.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try different characters, everyone with his unique set of stats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are four stats:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Effects</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you choose a balanced character or will you go with a specialized one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into <strong>Story Mode</strong>! Choose your favorite character and guide their unique journey to become the \"Ping Pong Master\". Face all other opponents in a series of matches enriched with fun dialogues that reveal the motivations and rivalries of each champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.poster.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.webm?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/9c03f639add3c6565f6ce1b7dfd4f1c4.mp4?t=1764933377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in split-screen with your friends for the best experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is nothing more satisfying than smashing the ball against your friend or hitting the edge of the table at the set point!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or Play Online with your Steam friends using Steam Remote Play Together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713750/extras/0c23c6a24cda88acfa0fa64171aa2880.avif?t=1764933377\" width=630 height=224 /></span></p>",
